{"lemma":"وارِد","slug":"وارِد","root":"#.ر.د","root_slug":"_-ر-د","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ر-د","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"وارِد","root":"ورد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n41860"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%90%D8%AF"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"one who descends, especially to a watering place"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"one who arrives in a place"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"one who leads his cattle to water"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"one who enters somewhere"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"present (as opposed to absent)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sudden inspiration, idea that arises spontaneously in the mind"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"one who marches at the head, who is the first to attack, a brave, bold man"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"path, road"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"imported, arrived"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n41860","headword_ar":"وَارِدٌ","root":"wrd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A man, and a camel, or other animal, (L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coming to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arriving at water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., whether he enter it or do not enter it; (L, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"war~aAdN","text_ar":"وَرَّادٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L, CK:) pl. of the former,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wur~aAdN","text_ar":"وُرَّادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAriduwna","text_ar":"وَارِدُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) and of the latter,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"war~aAduwna","text_ar":"وَرَّادُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirodN","text_ar":"وِرْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino manokumo A_il~aA waAriduhaA","text_ar":"اـِنْ مَنْكُمْ اـِلَّا وَارِدُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[Kur, xix. 72,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not any of you that shall not come to it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means, accord. to Th, that the Muslims shall come to hell with the unbelievers, but not enter it with them. (L.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariyqN waAridu","text_ar":"طَرِيقٌ وَارِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A road,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"way, by which people come to water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAdirN","text_ar":"صَادِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, A, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sdr","text_ar":"صدر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maworidN","text_ar":"مَوْرِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lhu SaAdirN walaA waAridN","text_ar":"مَا لهُ صَادِرٌ وَلَا وَارِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sdr","text_ar":"صدر"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAridN","text_ar":"وَارِدٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A preceder."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.) So (accord. to some, TA) in the Kur, xii. 19. (L.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAridN","text_ar":"وَارِدٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Courageous;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bold; forward in affairs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warodN","text_ar":"وَرْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEorN waAridN","text_ar":"شَعْرٌ وَارِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Long and lank hair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hair so long as to reach the buttocks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,) of a woman. (L.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAridN","text_ar":"وَارِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  Anything"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aronabapN waAridapN","text_ar":"اَرْنَبَةٌ وَارِدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The end,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tip, of a nose advancing over the middle of the mustaches:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L:) because the nose, when it is long, reaches to the water when the person drinks: and in like manner, a lip, and a gum. (L.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN waAridu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ وَارِدُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aronabapi","text_ar":"الاَرْنَبَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has a long end,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tip, to his nose."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ajarapN waAridapu AlA^agoSaAni","text_ar":"شَجَرَةٌ وَارِدَةُ الاَغْصَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tree having pendulous branches."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b5-  See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirodN","text_ar":"وِرْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["L","CK","S","Msb","K","A"]}]}}